Package: Parallelogram
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-12-23
Title: Parallelogram Method for On-leveling Earned Premium
Author: Benedict Escoto
Maintainer: Benedict Escoto <benedict.escoto@aonbenfield.com>
Depends: ggplot2, lubridate, plyr
Description: Implements the insurance-related actuarial technique
  called the Parallelogram Method.  This algorithm takes historical rate
  change information and computes rate levels and on-level premium.
  Variables rates of written premium are supported.
License: GPL (>= 2)
